# Go: every .go is generated by Fido Emit at build time, never checked in; the uncommittable-Go seal +
# ocaml-origin gate are the backstops.  (Only e2e/golden.* are tracked under e2e/.)
*.go
/fido
*.test
*.out
vendor/

# Extraction output + writer build artifacts (generated in the build, never tracked).
/emit_out.ml
/emit_out.mli
/fido_writer
*.cmi
*.cmo
*.cmx
*.cmxs
*.o

# Environment
.env

# Rocq build artifacts — .v sources are checked in, these are not
*.glob
*.vo
*.vok
*.vos
*.vio
*.aux
.*.aux
.lia.cache
.nia.cache
.coq-native/
_build/
